tag\" >Small, Experimental, and Unwaveringly Weird</h2>Offering 10 - 12 hours of playtime with a dozen boss encounters, friends to recruit, and visitors to invite back to your home, Look Outside offers different experiences for every player on their way to uncover several different endings.",
